1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,800
[Episode 31]

2
00:00:05,320 --> 00:00:06,330
Dopamine

3
00:00:06,580 --> 00:00:08,780
A substance secreted
when we feel happy

4
00:00:10,730 --> 00:00:11,790
But unfortunately

5
00:00:12,170 --> 00:00:13,570
We can never know

6
00:00:15,410 --> 00:00:17,690
How long our happiness

7
00:00:18,730 --> 00:00:20,910
Will actually last

8
00:00:22,530 --> 00:00:23,260
Or whether it

9
00:00:23,690 --> 00:00:26,690
Is just like a cold sparkler
only briefly shining

10
00:00:27,410 --> 00:00:28,940
Before fading into silence

11
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:37,170
You seem to be in a good mood

12
00:00:37,770 --> 00:00:38,900
Where have you been?

13
00:00:40,730 --> 00:00:41,890
Maybe because I'm happy

14
00:00:41,890 --> 00:00:42,210
Hmm

15
00:00:42,690 --> 00:00:44,690
Is it because you've fallen in love?

16
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:45,460
No

17
00:00:45,850 --> 00:00:46,780
It's because now

18
00:00:47,050 --> 00:00:48,780
I'm working on getting revenge

19
00:00:48,930 --> 00:00:50,650
Against the person who once made my life miserable

20
00:00:50,650 --> 00:00:52,690
Oh come on, it's been so long

21
00:00:52,770 --> 00:00:54,690
You still want revenge on Max?

22
00:00:55,490 --> 00:00:56,900
I will never forget

23
00:00:57,410 --> 00:00:58,880
Everything he did to me

24
00:01:05,410 --> 00:01:07,670
Interested in trying another sandwich?

25
00:01:08,170 --> 00:01:10,030
Oh my God, bro

26
00:01:10,410 --> 00:01:12,270
You're already out of detention?

27
00:01:12,380 --> 00:01:13,070
Yes

28
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:15,300
Someone just bailed us out

29
00:01:15,570 --> 00:01:17,570
And we weren't charged with dealing

30
00:01:19,490 --> 00:01:19,810
Hey

31
00:01:20,090 --> 00:01:21,289
Bin, I'm really sorry

32
00:01:21,330 --> 00:01:22,730
For getting you involved

33
00:01:23,530 --> 00:01:24,200
It's okay

34
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:25,810
At least we got out of trouble

35
00:01:25,810 --> 00:01:26,770
So this time

36
00:01:26,970 --> 00:01:28,170
Let me make it up to you

37
00:01:30,650 --> 00:01:32,160
I promise it won't go wrong this time

38
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:35,080
[To Be Continued]
